Welcome to the Student Management System

This is the home page of the application.

About Student Management System

The Student Management System is designed to efficiently manage student information, including their personal details, marks/grades, and overall academic performance. It provides features for adding, updating, and retrieving student data, allowing administrators and educators to keep track of students' progress and generate reports.

Features:

  • Student Registration: Add new students to the system with their personal details.
  • Marks/Grades Assignment: Assign marks or grades to students for different subjects.
  • Marks/Grades Update: Update or correct marks or grades for individual students.
  • Student Results: Retrieve and display the result of a student based on their ID.
  • Student Grade Calculation: Calculate and display the grade of a student based on their marks.
